# Required Page Sections — All Page Types

## Service Pages (ALL 10 must be present)

1. **Hero** — H1, intro paragraph (50–80 words), primary CTA button
2. **Service overview** — What's included, how it works (200+ words)
3. **Pricing / What to expect** — Transparent "from £X" with explanation
4. **Process steps** — Numbered 4–6 step walkthrough
5. **Why choose us** — Gas Safe, experience, ratings, insurance
6. **FAQ section** — MINIMUM 5 FAQs, each answer 80–150 words
7. **Related services** — Cards/links to 3–4 related service pages
8. **Areas covered** — Mention + link to all area pages
9. **Customer testimonial** — At least 1 relevant review
10. **CTA section** — Book now, call, WhatsApp with urgency messaging

## Area Pages (ALL 9 must be present)

1. **Hero** — H1 with area name + postcode, intro text
2. **Area description** — 150+ words about area, neighborhoods, landmarks
3. **Services available** — All services listed with links
4. **Response time** — "We reach [Area] in approximately X minutes"
5. **Postcodes covered** — Full list of postcodes in area
6. **Local testimonial** — Review from customer in that area
7. **Nearby areas** — Links to 3–4 adjacent area pages
8. **FAQ** — 3–5 area-specific questions with FAQPage schema
9. **CTA** — Area-personalized booking message

## Homepage (ALL 8 must be present)

1. **Hero** — H1, 50–80 word intro, primary + secondary CTA, trust badges
2. **Services grid** — All 10+ services as cards with image, title, 1-line description
3. **Offer/promo banner** — Key service with price (e.g. Boiler Service from £79)
4. **Why choose us** — 4 trust stats: 30+ Years / Gas Safe / 12+ Engineers / 4.6★
5. **Testimonials** — Minimum 5 reviews with name, area, star rating
6. **Areas we cover** — All 9 areas as linked cards with postcodes
7. **CTA section** — Book Now + WhatsApp + Call with urgency
8. **Footer NAP** — Full Name, Address, Phone, Email, Gas Safe reg

## Blog Posts (ALL 7 must be present)

1. **Hero** — H1 with long-tail keyword, published date, read time
2. **Introduction** — 80–120 words: problem, audience, what they'll learn
3. **Main body** — Minimum 3 H2 sections, each 200+ words
4. **Images** — At least 1 optimised image with descriptive alt text
5. **FAQ section** — Minimum 3 FAQs with FAQPage schema, each 80–150 words
6. **Related services** — Inline links to 2–3 service pages
7. **CTA** — "Need help? Book a [service] in Peterborough today"

## About Page (ALL 6 must be present)

1. **Hero** — H1: "About Peterborough Plumbers — 30+ Years..."
2. **Company story** — Founded when, how, why — 150+ words
3. **Team section** — Named engineers with Gas Safe credentials
4. **Accreditations** — Gas Safe logo + reg number, trade memberships
5. **Trust stats** — Years / engineers / reviews / areas covered
6. **CTA** — Book a job or get a quote

## Reviews Page (ALL 5 must be present)

1. **Hero** — H1: "Customer Reviews — Peterborough Plumbers | 4.6★ Google Rating"
2. **Aggregate score** — Large star rating + total count + platform
3. **Review cards** — Minimum 10 reviews: name, area, date, stars, full text
4. **Service filter** — Filter by service type (optional but ideal)
5. **CTA** — "Leave a review" + Google review link

## Blog Topic Priorities

1. "How Much Does [Service] Cost in Peterborough?" (cost guides)
2. "Signs Your [Thing] Needs [Service/Replacing]" (problem-aware)
3. "[Season] Plumbing Tips for Peterborough Homeowners" (seasonal)
4. "[Regulation] for Peterborough Landlords" (landlord-focused)
5. "What to Do When [Emergency Situation]" (emergency)
6. "[Option A] vs [Option B] — Which Is Right?" (comparison)
